---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Affiliate Disclosure - GlowPicked"
  description="Complete transparency about our affiliate relationships and how we earn commissions while maintaining honest reviews of beauty and skincare products."
  keywords="affiliate disclosure, transparency, honest reviews, commission disclosure"
  noIndex={true}
>
  <article class="legal-page">
    <div class="container">
      <header class="legal-header">
        <h1>Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
        <p class="last-updated">Last Updated: February 16, 2026</p>
        <p class="intro">
          At GlowPicked, transparency is one of our core values. We want you to know exactly how we operate 
          and how we earn money so you can trust our reviews and recommendations.
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="legal-content">
        <section class="disclosure-section">
          <h2>The Honest Truth About Our Affiliate Relationships</h2>
          
          <div class="truth-card">
            <h3>üí∞ Yes, We Earn Commissions</h3>
            <p>
              When you purchase a product through one of our links, we may earn a small commission from the retailer 
              (typically 1-10% of the purchase price). This doesn't cost you anything extra - it's how retailers 
              pay us for sending customers their way.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="truth-card">
            <h3>ü§ñ Our Research Process Is Transparent</h3>
            <p>
              We do NOT buy or physically test products. Instead, we use AI tools to research Amazon customer reviews 
              and present honest recommendations based on what real buyers say. 
              This means our insights are based on thousands of real human experiences ‚Äî not just one person's opinion. 
              Our systems prioritize product quality over profit potential.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="how-it-works">
          <h2>How Our Review Process Actually Works</h2>
          
          <div class="process-steps">
            <div class="step">
              <div class="step-number">1</div>
              <div class="step-content">
                <h3>Product Selection</h3>
                <p>We pick products based on high ratings and positive customer reviews ‚Äî not commission rates.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="step">
              <div class="step-number">2</div>
              <div class="step-content">
                <h3>AI Review Analysis</h3>
                <p>We research Amazon customer reviews, looking at ratings, review volume, and common feedback themes.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="step">
              <div class="step-number">3</div>
              <div class="step-content">
                <h3>Honest Recommendations</h3>
                <p>We publish honest recommendations based on real Amazon customer reviews ‚Äî not personal testing.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="step">
              <div class="step-number">4</div>
              <div class="step-content">
                <h3>Affiliate Links</h3>
                <p>We add affiliate links to products our analysis genuinely recommends, earning a commission if you choose to buy.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="partners-section">
          <h2>Our Affiliate Partners</h2>
          
          <div class="partner-list">
            <div class="partner">
              <h3>Amazon Associates</h3>
              <p class="amazon-associate-disclaimer">As an Amazon Associate we earn from qualifying purchases.</p>
              <p>
                We participate in the Amazon Associates Program. When you click on an Amazon product link 
                and make a purchase, we earn a small commission (typically 1-10% depending on the product category).
              </p>
              <div class="commission-rate">Beauty Products: ~4-8% commission</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="partner">
              <h3>Direct Brand Partnerships</h3>
              <p>
                We may occasionally partner directly with beauty brands for affiliate commissions. 
                Any such relationships will be clearly disclosed in the specific review.
              </p>
              <div class="commission-rate">Varies by brand: 2-15% commission</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="what-this-means">
          <h2>What This Means for You</h2>
          
          <div class="benefit-cards">
            <div class="benefit-card positive">
              <div class="benefit-icon">‚úÖ</div>
              <div class="benefit-content">
                <h3>You Pay Nothing Extra</h3>
                <p>Affiliate commissions don't increase the price you pay. The retailer pays us from their profit margin.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="benefit-card positive">
              <div class="benefit-icon">‚úÖ</div>
              <div class="benefit-content">
                <h3>It Funds Our Research</h3>
                <p>Commissions help us keep this site running and continue researching products.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="benefit-card positive">
              <div class="benefit-icon">‚úÖ</div>
              <div class="benefit-content">
                <h3>Reviews Stay Honest</h3>
                <p>We try to only recommend products with consistently positive reviews. We include budget options alongside luxury ones.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="benefit-card neutral">
              <div class="benefit-icon">‚ÑπÔ∏è</div>
              <div class="benefit-content">
                <h3>We Have a Financial Incentive</h3>
                <p>When you buy through our links, we earn money. We're transparent about this potential bias so you can factor it into your decision.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="commitment-section">
          <h2>Our Commitment to You</h2>
          
          <div class="commitment-list">
            <div class="commitment-item">
              <h3>üéØ Honest Reviews Always</h3>
              <p>
                We'll never recommend a product just because it has high commission rates. 
                Our recommendations are based on real Amazon customer reviews.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="commitment-item">
              <h3>üìä Honest Recommendations</h3>
              <p>
                We pick products based on customer feedback, not profit potential. 
                We frequently recommend cheaper alternatives when they work just as well.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="commitment-item">
              <h3>üîç Clear Disclosures</h3>
              <p>
                We'll always clearly mark affiliate links and disclose any potential conflicts of interest 
                in our reviews and articles.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="commitment-item">
              <h3>üîç Independent Analysis</h3>
              <p>
                We aim to evaluate products independently of affiliate relationships, 
                ensuring unbiased recommendations.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="legal-requirements">
          <h2>Legal Requirements & Compliance</h2>
          
          <div class="compliance-info">
            <h3>FTC Guidelines</h3>
            <p>
              We comply with Federal Trade Commission (FTC) guidelines regarding affiliate disclosures. 
              The FTC requires that we clearly and conspicuously disclose our affiliate relationships.
            </p>
            
            <h3>Canadian Regulations</h3>
            <p>
              As a Canadian-operated website, we also comply with Competition Bureau Canada guidelines 
              for advertising and affiliate marketing disclosure requirements.
            </p>
            
            <h3>Ongoing Compliance</h3>
            <p>
              We regularly review our disclosure practices to ensure compliance with evolving regulations 
              in both the United States and Canada.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="questions-section">
          <h2>Questions About Our Affiliate Relationships?</h2>
          
          <div class="faq-list">
            <div class="faq-item">
              <h3>Q: Do you only review products with affiliate programs?</h3>
              <p>
                <strong>A:</strong> No. We review products based on user interest and scientific merit. 
                If a great product doesn't have an affiliate program, we'll still review it honestly 
                and link to it without earning a commission.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
              <h3>Q: Are your negative reviews fake to make positive ones seem more credible?</h3>
              <p>
                <strong>A:</strong> Absolutely not. We publish negative analysis because data shows products genuinely disappoint reviewers. We include this to save you money and maintain credibility.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
              <h3>Q: How do I know which links are affiliate links?</h3>
              <p>
                <strong>A:</strong> We clearly mark affiliate links and include disclosure statements 
                at the top of every article. When in doubt, assume any product link earns us a commission.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
              <h3>Q: Can I support your work without buying through affiliate links?</h3>
              <p>
                <strong>A:</strong> Yes! Share our articles with friends, follow us on social media, 
                and subscribe to our newsletter. Word-of-mouth recommendations help us grow more than commissions.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="contact-section">
          <h2>Still Have Questions?</h2>
          <p>
            If you have any questions about our affiliate relationships, review process, or business model, 
            we're happy to answer them. Transparency is important to us.
          </p>
          <a href="mailto:contact@glowpicked.com" class="contact-button">Contact Us</a>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>

